{"tid":89062,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】【孝子現身】收樓做禮物自住 退休爸爸：囝囝出首期仲供埋樓！","createTime":"2017-01-21T05:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T06:41:43.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb77e34b7526c573a75c3fa6805caeeeb2b71147","tid":89062,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:59:39.000Z","msg":"【短片】【孝子現身】收樓做禮物自住 退休爸爸：囝囝出首期仲供埋樓！<br />\n<br />\n中海外（688）啟德1號2期早前推出122伙，安排今日早上進行次輪銷售；近期一直都是慈父慈母出錢又出力，買樓送給囝女，但今次售樓現場卻反高潮，出現孝子買樓送給退休爸爸劇情！<br />\n<br />\n抽到16號前籌的啟德1號2期買家林先生表示，是兒子買給他，用作自住，買的是細單位，自己本身無物業，所以無需付稅，首期同供樓都由兒子負責。他認為區域配套好，交通方便，潛力好。<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃嘉銘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56203360&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56203360%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170121&d=w5yGqUan81Y6HPaDGCH1WXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d5ceba93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56203360%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170121&h=44f692fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56203360&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170121</a><br />\n<br />\n//子幹撚，呢個老豆要屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f8380b4b726e356d9fe2602c161ae90895d973","tid":89062,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"成功靠兒幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87565f5375b5d08e1faf1a5c0ded4f5a1ca2a86d","tid":89062,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"又賣晒，幾個鐘，全部香港身份證持有人"},{"p